---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout>
    <main
        class="flex items-start justify-start flex-col gap-4 py-12 px-4 md:px-0 md:w-2/5 w-full"
    >
        <h1 class="font-bold w-full text-justify">{"%"} ls facts</h1>

        <p class="text-sm w-full text-justify">
            I graduated from <span class="font-bold">UC Berkeley</span> with a B.S.
            in Electrical Engineering and Computer Sciences (Honors) and a Minor in
            Public Policy, in 2.5 years.
        </p>

        <p class="text-sm w-full text-justify">
            I was an undergraduate machine learning researcher advised by <a
                href="https://ritwikgupta.me/"
                target="_blank"
                class="underline text-blue-500">Dr. Ritwik Gupta</a
            > and <a
                href="https://camallen.net/"
                target="_blank"
                class="underline text-blue-500">Dr. Cam Allen</a
            > at
            <a
                href="https://bair.berkeley.edu/"
                target="_blank"
                class="underline text-blue-500">BAIR</a
            > and <a
                href="https://humancompatible.ai/"
                target="_blank"
                class="underline text-blue-500">CHAI</a
            >.
        </p>

        <p class="text-sm w-full text-justify">
            I was a research fellow at <span class="font-bold">OpenAI</span> in Fall
            2025 as part of their Launchpad program. Participation, at least for the
            inaugural batch which I was part of, was invite-only.
        </p>

        <p class="text-sm w-full text-justify">
            I've published workshop papers at <span class="font-bold"
                >NeurIPS</span
            > and <span class="font-bold">ICML</span>, and contributed to a
            chapter in a soon-to-be-published technical AI safety book. You can
            find my papers on my <a
                href="https://scholar.google.com/citations?user=6CbTfzIAAAAJ&hl=en&oi=ao"
                target="_blank"
                class="underline text-blue-500">Google Scholar</a
            >. I'm still actively doing research (as a hobby / side hustle, if
            you will)!
        </p>

        <p class="text-sm w-full text-justify">
            I'm a history buff. Currently reading <span class="italic"
                >The Hamilton Scheme</span
            > by William Hogeland. My favorite historical figure is Alexander Hamilton.
            Planning to read more into military history once I'm done with the aforementioned
            book!
        </p>

        <p class="text-sm w-full text-justify">
            I'm a guilty perpetuator of the CS nerd stereotype of liking
            climbing. I'm on V4/V5 walls now <span class="text-gray-300"
                >(my fingers need help)</span
            >. I also play volleyball, basketball, netball, table tennis, and
            badminton.
        </p>

        <p class="text-sm w-full text-justify">
            I draw manga! A lot of my inspiration comes from <span
                class="italic">DBZ</span
            >, both art style- and story-wise. Other influences include <span
                class="italic">Naruto</span
            > and <span class="italic">Haikyu</span>.
        </p>

        <p class="text-sm w-full text-justify">
            I was born in Jakarta, Indonesia. I then moved to Singapore when I
            was 12. Now you can spot me around the Bay Area.
        </p>

        <p class="text-xs w-full text-justify">
            <a href="/" class="underline text-blue-500">{"<"} ctrl + c</a>
        </p>
    </main>
</Layout>
